    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i see. i'm a bit worried about some of our younger execs though. we have some people of color coming into leadership roles, and i want to make sure they don't run into issues with what people perceive as \"professional.\" like, how should they handle hair textures that aren't naturally smooth or straight if they're trying to hit that \"polished\" look you mentioned?",
