      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "The key for textured hair is masterful execution and definition, ensuring it looks intentionally styled rather than simply textured. Investing in professional grooming consultations specifically tailored to textured hair can help develop personalized, impeccably maintained styles. The goal is neatness and deliberate polish, similar to how smooth hair is controlled; ask stylists to focus on sleekness, definition, and sharpness of the edges. When approached with intention, textured hairstyles can project confidence and strength just as effectively as traditional styles.",
